cs.IR, cs.DL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DB 

The paper discusses issues related to knowledge organization systems and information retrieval, which are closely related to the field of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The use of faceted classifications is also relevant to Digital Libraries (cs.DL) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) as they involve organizing and retrieving information. The author also mentions the use of machine processing, which is a key aspect of Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Database Systems (cs.DB).
